title: 820-00165  only works with charger
message:
The macbook air  had previously entered due to the same problem, diode d7005 was changed, now the same diode fails again
these are measurements

with only battery

title: 820-00165  only works with charger
message:
To avoid future problems, change all 3 C7090-92.
And now need to change D7005, of course.

Be sure no short at 3V3_G3H to ground (L7095).
